{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"stdDeviation","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stdDeviation","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n<p><code>stdDeviation</code> 属性定义了模糊操作的标准差。如果列出两个 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">&lt;number&gt; (en-US)</a>，第一个数字表示沿着 x 轴的标准差值，第二个值表示沿着 y 轴的标准差值。如果只出现一个数字，那个值就表示在 x 轴和 y 轴上有着相同的标准差。</p>\n<p>负值是不允许的。设为零即禁用了已有滤镜的原本效果（比如，结果是滤镜输入图像）。如果 <code>stdDeviation</code> 在 x 轴和 y 轴上只有一个为 0，那么模糊效果就只会应用于非 0 的那个方向。</p>\n<p>如果此属性没被定义，就与标准差值被定义为 0 的效果一样。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>类别</th>\n      <th>None</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>值</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Content_type#number-optional-number\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">&lt;number-optional-number&gt; (en-US)</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>可变性</td>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table><dl>\n  <dt id=\"number-optional-number_2\">&lt;number-optional-number&gt;</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A pair of &lt;number&gt;s, where the second &lt;number&gt; is optional.</p>\n    <pre class=\"notranslate\">number-optional-number ::= number\n                            | number, number\n</pre>\n    <p>In the SVG DOM, a &lt;number-optional-number&gt; is represented using a pair of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedInteger\"><code>SVGAnimatedInteger</code></a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedNumber\"><code>SVGAnimatedNumber</code></a> objects.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下的元素可以使用 <code>stdDeviation</code> 属性</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feGaussianBlur\"><code>&lt;feGaussianBlur&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[],"query":"svg.elements.feGaussianBlur.stdDeviation"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"stdDeviation","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/stddeviation","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/stddeviation/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG：可缩放矢量图形"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stdDeviation","title":"stdDeviation"}],"pageTitle":"stdDeviation - SVG：可缩放矢量图形 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}